## PGroonga — Multilingual Full Text Search

**When you need it**: Full-text search for Japanese, Chinese, Korean, Arabic, or any non-English language. Built-in `tsvector` uses English stemming and doesn't handle these languages well.

```sql
CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgroonga WITH SCHEMA extensions;

-- Add PGroonga index (replaces tsvector for non-English)
CREATE INDEX products_name_pgroonga ON products USING pgroonga(name);

-- Search (works for ANY language)
SELECT * FROM products WHERE name &@ '検索';          -- Japanese
SELECT * FROM products WHERE name &@ 'أنتروبيك';      -- Arabic
SELECT * FROM products WHERE name &@~ 'search AND AI'; -- Boolean search

-- Also works for English with better stemming than tsvector
```

