## Extensions Quick Reference (updated V23)

| Extension | Key use | Enable |
|---|---|---|
| `vector` | AI/semantic search, embeddings | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector` |
| `pg_cron` | Scheduled jobs | Pre-installed |
| `pg_net` | HTTP calls from DB triggers | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_net` |
| `pgmq` | Background job queues | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgmq` |
| `pg_stat_statements` | Slow query analysis | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_stat_statements` |
| `index_advisor` | Missing index suggestions | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS index_advisor` |
| `hypopg` | Test indexes safely | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS hypopg` |
| `pg_jsonschema` | Validate JSONB structure | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_jsonschema` |
| `pg_hashids` | Short public-facing IDs | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_hashids` |
| `pg_graphql` | Auto GraphQL API | Pre-installed (disable if unused) |
| `pg_trgm` | Fuzzy text search, ILIKE with index | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_trgm` |
| `pgroonga` | Non-English full-text search | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgroonga` |
| `pgaudit` | Compliance audit logging | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgaudit` |
| `postgis` | Geospatial / location queries | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS postgis` |
| `pg_repack` | Reclaim storage bloat | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pg_repack` |
| `wrappers` | Foreign Data Wrappers (Stripe, Firebase, S3) | `CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS wrappers` |
